{"tid":838424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「反黑警司」認受賄 收57萬元向夜場經營者洩警行動機密","createTime":"2018-09-27T06:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:07:39.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab6f95743ca3da36385089805178fa49c7b2a10","tid":838424,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538017412_8cc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538017412_8cc7.jpg&h=dc937642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">被告吳偉漢(資料圖片)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有「反黑警司」之稱的港島總區刑事總部警司吳偉漢，涉自2015年底起收受兩會所的經營者78萬元及免費嫖妓服務，向兩人洩露警方調查兩會所及行動的機密資料。吳與兩經營者遭檢控，三人經認罪協商後今在區院各承認一項罪名，其中吳承認5次收款，每次收取11.4萬元賄款，即共約57萬元，但否認接受免費嫖妓服務的相關控罪，而吳於今年5月已表達認罪意向並放棄保釋，當時遭即時收押。<br />\n<br />\n被告吳偉漢（53歲）、經營MB Club Mont. Busa（MBC）及GOLDEN夜總會的欒其祥（46歲）與謝凱健（37歲）。<br />\n<br />\n吳偉漢及欒其祥現承認一項串謀使公職人員接受利益罪，謝凱健則承認一項協助和教唆他人向公職人員提供利益罪。控罪指吳與欒於2015年11月至2017年1月串謀使身為警務處警司的吳，於2016年1月、5月、9月、11月及2017年1月，5次接受欒每次提供的11.4萬元，作為吳作向對方披露有關警方調查MB Club Mont. Busa及GOLDEN的機密資料，並會提供意見的報酬。另謝於2017年1月協助教唆欒向吳提供11.4萬元利益。<br />\n<br />\n3人原被被控8項控罪，包括串謀使公職人員接受利益、公職人員收受利益、向公職人員提供利益、串謀犯公職人員行為失當罪等，其中5項為交替控罪。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCCC1046/17】<br />\n<br />\n記者蔡少玲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58728494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728494&d=qy6Ry%2FISLpotfIeQJdc3d5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a31cf4a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728494&h=35014c02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58728494</a>"},{"pid":"cf65f16a2a6f8c732519559d9fd064238404419f","tid":838424,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"向警賊致敬又多一員"},{"pid":"538009b2a513b94a3c6dda10cdda2ee36c6532b1","tid":838424,"uid":196753,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"三哥"},{"pid":"a926684b469266953365b0e6f7d295a23f8aba0e","tid":838424,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"阿Sir收規唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d3581dcdc9959ca82f3acd0aa01e8a5632eae","tid":838424,"uid":132557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"你地無做錯到.JPG"},{"pid":"9d238c6a0f6d2f96dfc48776e63ba5ac425c3576","tid":838424,"uid":132557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"呀處長又行出黎 警方會全力提供支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b289a66980405fe3f4e458612db70fd3b54a5051","tid":838424,"uid":39200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"個官都唔體諒下人地其實一家人, 唔好咁斤斤計較啦"},{"pid":"a79f1afd29b4e6920602db5a76fcc02fe7fb9ad8","tid":838424,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d238c6a0f6d2f96dfc48776e63ba5ac425c3576","tid":838424,"uid":132557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"呀處長又行出黎 警方會全力提供支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"我地絕不容許警隊有害群之馬<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n不過現時睇黎警隊並冇害群之馬"},{"pid":"cc11866a3e40e4c08e8cb6875baf02681363bb42","tid":838424,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"警察 = 垃圾"},{"pid":"cc1141c8feb76c1306dcb760e52edc8808b6f986","tid":838424,"uid":66784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"締聽岀黎講兩句"},{"pid":"a2f44b60574b9a166db9000756e3355f9f3c8450","tid":838424,"uid":